To use Windows 365 Enterprise, each user needs to be licensed for:    • Windows 11 Enterprise or Windows 10 Enterprise and Intune and Azure Active Directory P1    or    • One of the following versions of Microsoft 365: Business Premium, A3, A5, E3, E5, or F3 (including Microsoft 365 Education Student Use Benefit subscriptions)    Securely stream your Windows experience - including your personalized apps, content, and settings – from the Microsoft cloud to any device with your Windows 365 Cloud PC.
